   "source": [
    "Task\n",
    "The provided code stub reads an integer, n, from STDIN. For all non-negative integers , print i < n.print i*i.\n",
    "\n",
    "Example\n",
    "n=3\n",
    "The list of non-negative integers that are less than n=3 is [0,1,2]. Print the square of each number on a separate line.\n",
    "0\n",
    "1\n",
    "4\n",
    "\n",
    "Input Format\n",
    "\n",
    "The first and only line contains the integer, n.\n",
    "\n",
    "Constraints\n",
    "1 <= n <= 20\n",
    "\n",
    "Output Format\n",
    "\n",
    "Print  lines, one corresponding to each i.\n",
    "\n",
    "Sample Input 0\n",
    "5\n",
    "\n",
    "Sample Output 0\n",
    "0\n",
    "1\n",
    "4\n",
    "9\n",
    "16"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 1,
   "id": "c3a90720-5567-40dc-a3bb-78c0a3ae8bee",
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [
